cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a new learning algorithm that improves upon the popular SVM method by optimizing the margin distribution. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method can also be applied to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE) which are closely related to machine learning. Additionally, the paper discusses the theoretical and empirical superiority of the proposed method, which could fall under the category of statistical learning (cs.SI).
